      "id": "standard_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_1",
      "description": "This car is in fair condition. It runs and drives, but shows noticeable wear both inside and out. Expect some cosmetic blemishes on the exterior, worn interior surfaces, and potentially some minor mechanical issues that may need attention. It's a functional vehicle suitable for a buyer willing to accept its current state or put in some work.",
